\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-773c4c0\" data-id=\"773c4c0\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b071b1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b071b1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A Training program to develop community leaders<\/span><\/h5>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98187ce elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"98187ce\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Program Details<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2dd35e0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2dd35e0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Leadership Beaver Dam: Where Leaders Rise, Communities Thrive.<\/p><p>Are you ready to unlock your full potential and make a lasting impact in Beaver Dam and beyond? Look no further than the Leadership Beaver Dam Program!<\/p><p>Our program is designed to empower individuals like you to become more knowledgeable and effective leaders in every aspect of your life \u2013 as parents, employees, employers, citizens, volunteers, and neighbors. Through a series of engaging classes and community projects, you&#8217;ll gain valuable insights into the areas of our community that touch your life every day.<\/p><p>By the end of the program, you&#8217;ll have had the opportunity to connect with dozens of passionate, intelligent, and motivated individuals who share your commitment to making a difference. These new contacts can serve as invaluable advisors and mentors, both personally and professionally, long after you&#8217;ve completed the program.<\/p><p>Throughout your journey with Leadership Beaver Dam, you&#8217;ll be involved in hands-on community projects that allow you to put your newfound knowledge and skills into action. From designing and implementing initiatives to addressing real-world challenges, you&#8217;ll have the chance to make a tangible difference in our community.<\/p><p>Our curriculum is carefully crafted to cover a wide range of topics, including leadership and communication styles, the rich history of Beaver Dam, government and nonprofits, health and wellness, businesses, education, stewardship, and more. With nine total classes, you&#8217;ll delve deep into these subjects and emerge with a comprehensive understanding of what it takes to lead effectively in today&#8217;s world.<\/p><p>Join us on this transformative journey and discover the leader within you. Together, we&#8217;ll shape the future of Beaver Dam and create a stronger, more vibrant community for generations to come.<\/p><p>Ready to take the next step? Apply for Leadership Beaver Dam today and embark on a life-changing experience!\u00a0 Mark your calendar for Setember 10, October 8, November 12 and December 10 in 2025 and January 14, February 11, March 11, April 8 and May 13 in 2026<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-1fa4cf7\" data-id=\"1fa4cf7\" data-element_t